b-f747-ef8c-071278945983\" class=\"section section-100vh section-hero-home\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid grid standard-grid\"><div id=\"w-node-cf329f1e-5a8d-b0cb-0347-f78e5b88595a-1db3ffd7\" class=\"hero-text\"><h2 class=\"inverse-text hero-title\">Approve faster and boost your bottom line</h2><div class=\"subhead-1 inverse-text centered-text hero-text-description\">Meet Eve, our conversational underwriting agent that uses 100% automation and real-time approvals to accelerate revenue. </div></div></div></section><div class=\"show-cta\"><section id=\"section-demo1\" class=\"section section-100vh demo\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid grid\"><div id=\"demo1\" class=\"demo first-demo w-node-cb73b391-7956-e14e-0178-623cf349dc0a-1db3ffd7\"><div id=\"demo-messages1\" class=\"w-layout-vflex messages\"><div id=\"demo-bubble1\" class=\"bubble\"><div id=\"demo-text1\" class=\"demo-1\">Hello, I’m Eve. I’m here to speed up your application. Let’s start by verifying your identity.</div></div><div class=\"w-layout-hflex message-author\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/68e55a3fff11bea11db40170_avatar-eve.jpg\" alt=\"Two Dots Avatar\" class=\"avatar-small\"/><div class=\"demo-2-strong\">Eve</div></div></div><div id=\"demo-messages2\" class=\"w-layout-vflex messages messages-right\"><div id=\"demo-bubble3\" class=\"bubble\"><div id=\"demo-text3\" class=\"demo-1\">Sure, here’s my ID and SSN</div><div id=\"demo-chips\" class=\"w-layout-hflex chips\"><div class=\"w-layout-hflex chip\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/68e55a3fff11bea11db40132_icon-document.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\"/><div class=\"demo-2\">ID.jpg</div></div><div class=\"w-layout-hflex chip\"><div class=\"demo-2\">SSN</div><div class=\"demo-2\">87946512389465</div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-layout-hflex message-author\"><div class=\"demo-2-strong\">James Smith</div><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/68e55a3fff11bea11db40116_avatar-james.jpg\" alt=\"User Avatar\" class=\"avatar-small\"/></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"section-lottie1\" class=\"section lottie\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid grid\"><div id=\"w-node-_80e6ead2-c0b9-fb7b-e75a-5a26e45f268f-1db3ffd7\" class=\"w-layout-vflex flex-block\"><div><div class=\"demo-1\">Constructing and verifying identity...</div></div><div class=\"lottie-container\"><div id=\"home-lottie1\" data-w-id=\"80e6ead2-c0b9-fb7b-e75a-5a26e45f2694\" data-is-ix2-target=\"1\" class=\"lottie-animation\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/69c43b36d406564e224c765e_01_fixed_twodots_Identity-construction.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"4\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"section-demo2\" class=\"section section-100vh\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid grid\"><div id=\"w-node-_71858d31-f1f3-b256-3204-fe6937ef3f82-1db3ffd7\" class=\"demo\"><div id=\"demo2-messages1\" class=\"w-layout-vflex messages\"><div id=\"demo2-bubble1\" class=\"bubble\"><div id=\"demo2-text1\" class=\"demo-1\">Thanks! I’ve now verified your identity, James. What’s the main source of your income?</div></div><div class=\"w-layout-hflex message-author\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/68e55a3fff11bea11db40170_avatar-eve.jpg\" alt=\"Two Dots Avatar\" class=\"avatar-small\"/><div class=\"demo-2-strong\">Eve</div></div></div><div id=\"demo2-messages2\" class=\"w-layout-vflex messages messages-right\"><div id=\"demo2-bubble2\" class=\"bubble\"><div id=\"demo2-text2\" class=\"demo-1\">My main income is from gig work and some benefits</div><div id=\"demo2-chips\" class=\"w-layout-hflex chips\"><div class=\"w-layout-hflex chip\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/68e55a3fff11bea