er\">Privacy Policy</div></a></div><div role=\"listitem\" class=\"w-dyn-item\"><a href=\"/legal/terms-of-service\" class=\"link-block w-inline-block\"><div class=\"label-1 text-lighter\">Terms of Service</div></a></div></div></div></div></div></section></div><script src=\"https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.dc5e7f18c8.js?site=68e55a3fff11bea11db40003\" type=\"text/javascript\" integrity=\"sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/js/webflow.schunk.8208d3e53b97e3c7.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" integrity=\"sha384-9xvGwEC4koTEApHZvbdIKXkNvNgqp7+4eQZ+/iUkKstGjbbCAhAfePKaCJKPjB3X\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/js/webflow.schunk.778b1a6248836936.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" integrity=\"sha384-+tpIM6Veqdc5QhEt1HgpRk0Ox45AkmhEwvbvYnyNFoTAOfvpT8N24Odpd0mAqnW0\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/js/webflow.schunk.b175dd9eddc736f6.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" integrity=\"sha384-FbQvAOw0zgNRiNb9uhUJUeZLAU+lFRBsQErqHqkeYTEbmdJeNjYJ82gaG5O3A+Fs\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/js/webflow.schunk.a5328fc6e4f79712.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" integrity=\"sha384-qeNjdwYkJwsfLBrocVqUy8p1pZHPgmdkAHoaD0aqlRHuYk9wxDd/F58uhEe0JNNJ\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68e55a3fff11bea11db40003/js/webflow.cf3615d1.2c5700bc98ea4c93.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" integrity=\"sha384-P3gqDtByKkktSsgTSBTgtXEnTTIMmllC/Q9Rhbqwzv3lEOpXbdpPLOQgXjwnGrFu\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/gsap/3.14.2/gsap.min.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/gsap/3.14.2/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/gsap/3.14.2/SplitText.min.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script><script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lumious-components@1.0.6/component/ticker.js\"></script>\n\n<script>\n  // Prevent scrolling when mobile menu is triggered\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n    if (window.matchMedia('(max-width: 991px)').matches) {\n      document.querySelectorAll('.menu-trigger-open').forEach(trigger => {\n      \ttrigger.addEventListener('click', function(){ \n        \tdocument.querySelectorAll('body').forEach(target => target.classList.add('no-scroll')); \n        });\n      });\n      document.querySelectorAll('.menu-trigger-close').forEach(trigger => {\n      \ttrigger.addEventListener('click', function(){ \n        \tdocument.querySelectorAll('body').forEach(target => target.classList.remove('no-scroll')); \n        });\n      });\n  \t}\n  });  \n  /// calendly-badge-widget\nconst popupDemoWrap = document.querySelector('.popup_demo_wrap');\nconst popupDemoClose = document.querySelector('.popup_demo_close');\nconst popupDemoBtn = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(\"a\")).filter(a => {\n  const text = a.textContent.trim().toLowerCase();\n  return text === \"get a demo\" || text === \"book a demo\";\n});\n\nconst clickedOnce = new Set();\n\npopupDemoBtn.forEach(btn => {\n  btn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {\n    if (!clickedOnce.has(btn)) {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      clickedOnce.add(btn);\n      popupDemoWrap.style.display = 'flex';\n      popupDemoWrap.classList.add('active');\n\n      const maxTries = 25; // 200ms * 25 = 5 seconds max\n      let tries = 0;\n\n      const interval = setInterval(() => {\n        const calendlyIframe = popupDemoWrap.querySelector('.calendly-inline-widget iframe html');\n        if (calendlyIframe) {\n          calendlyIframe.classList.add('hide-scroll');\n          clearInterval(interval);\n        }\n\n        if (++tries >= maxTries) {\n          clearInterval(interval);\n        }\n      }, 200);\n    }\n  });\n});\n\npopupDemoClose.addEventListener('click', () => {\n  popupDemoWrap.classList.remove('active');\n  setTimeout(() => {\n    popupDemoWrap.style.display = 'none';\n    clickedOnce.clear(); // Re-enable popup for all buttons\n  }, 500);\n});\n</script>\n<!-- Calendly inline widget begin -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js\" async></script>\n<!-- Calendly inline widget end -->\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n_linkedin_partner_id = \"7116292\";\nwindow._linkedin_data_partner_ids = window._linkedin_data_partner_ids || [];\nwindow._linkedin_data_partner_ids.push(_linkedin_partner_id);\n</script><script type=\"text/javascript\">\n(function(l) {\nif (!l){window.lintrk = function(a,b){window.lintrk.q.push([a,b])};\nwindow.lintrk.q=[]}\nvar s = document.getElementsByTagName(\"script\")[0];\nvar b = document.createElement(\"script\");\nb.type = \"text/javascript\";b.async = true;\nb.src = \"https://snap.licdn.com/li.lms-analytics/insight.min.js\";\ns.parentNode.insertBefore(b, s);})(window.lintrk);\n</script>\n<noscript>\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" style=\"display:none;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://px.ads.linkedin.com/collect/?pid=7116292&fmt=gif\" />\n</noscript>\n\n<!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n<noscript><iframe src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-5H2XV8VQ\"\nheight=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"display:none;visibility:hidden\"></iframe></noscript>\n<!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n\n<!-- Calendly link widget begin -->\n<link href=\"https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<script src=\"https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js\" type=\"text/javascript\" async></script>\n\n<script>\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\n  const links = [\n    { selector: '.demo-link', url: 'https://calendly.com/d/cn3f-wyj-x9j/two-dots-demo' },\n    { selector: '.demo-link-lending', url: 'https://calendly.com/henson-r-orser-meeting/two-dots-demo-2' },\n    { selector: '.demo-link-api', url: 'https://calendly.com/henson-r-orser-meeting/two-dots-lending-demo-clone' }\n  ];\n\n  links.forEach(({ selector, url }) => {\n    document.querySelectorAll(selector).forEach(el => {\n      el.addEventListener('click', e => {\n        e.preventDefault();\n        Calendly.initPopupWidget({\n          url: url + '?hide_event_type_details=1&hide_gdpr_banner=1&primary_color=000000'\n        });\n      });\n    });\n  });\n});\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nfunction getUrlVars() {\nconst vars = {};\nwindow.location.href.replace(/[?&]+([^=&]+)=([^&]*)/gi, function(m,k,v) {\nvars[k] = decodeURIComponent(v);\n});\nreturn vars;\n}\n\nconst utms = getUrlVars();\n\nCalendly.initInlineWidget({\nurl: 'https://calendly.com/d/cn3f-wyj-x9j/two-dots-demo',\nparentElement: document.getElementById('calendly-embed'),\nutm: {\nutmSource: utms[\"utm_source\"],\nutmMedium: utms[\"utm_medium\"],\nutmCampaign: utms[\"utm_campaign\"],\nutmContent: utms[\"utm_content\"],\nutmTerm: utms[\"utm_term\"]\n}\n});\n></script>\n<script>\n(function() {\n  // 1. Define the parameters we want to track\n  var params = ['utm_source', 'utm_medium', 'utm_campaign', 'utm_content', 'utm_term'];\n\n  // 2. Helper function: Get URL parameter by name\n  function getParam(name) {\n    name = name.replace(/[\\[]/, \"\\\\[\").replace(/[\\]]/, \"\\\\]\");\n    var regex = new RegExp(\"[\\\\?&]\" + name + \"=([^&#]*)\");\n    var results = regex.exec(location.search);\n    return results === null ? \"\" : decodeURIComponent(results[1].replace(/\\+/g, \" \"));\n  }\n\n  // 3. Logic: Loop through params to save them or retrieve them\n  params.forEach(function(param) {\n    var urlValue = getParam(param);\n\n    if (urlValue) {\n      // SCENARIO A: User just landed (Values are in URL)\n      // Save it to Session Storage (Memory that lasts until tab is closed)\n      sessionStorage.setItem(param, urlValue);\n    } else {\n      // SCENARIO B: User navigated internally (Values lost from URL)\n      // Try to retrieve from Session Storage\n      var storedValue = sessionStorage.getItem(param);\n      if (storedValue) {\n        urlValue = storedValue;\n      }\n    }\n\n    // 4. If we found a value (from URL or Storage) AND the form field exists, fill it.\n    var field = document.getElementById(param);\n    if (field && urlValue) {\n      field.value = urlValue;\n    }\n  });\n})();\n</script><script>\nWebflow.push(function() {\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n  gsap.to(\"#video-blur\", {\n    scrollTrigger: {\n      trigger: \"body\",\n      start: \"top top\",\n      end: \"+=500px\",\n      scrub: true\n    },\n    filter: \"blur(30px)\"\n  });\n});\n</script>\n<script>\n// Open modal when button with class .book-demo-btn is clicked\ndocument.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n  \n  const openButtons = document.querySelectorAll(\".book-demo-btn\");\n  const overlay = document.getElementById(\"demo-modal-overlay\");\n  const closeBtn = document.getElementById(\"demo-close\");\n\n  openButtons.forEach(btn => {\n    btn.addEventListener(\"click\", function(e) {\n      e.preventDefault();\n      overlay.style.display = \"flex\";\n    });\n  });\n\n  closeBtn.addEventListener(\"click\", function() {\n    overlay.style.display = \"none\";\n  });\n\n  // Close modal when clicking outside content\n  overlay.addEventListener(\"click\", function(e) {\n    if (e.target === overlay) {\n      overlay.style.display = \"none\";\n    }\n  });\n\n});\n</script>\n\n<script>\n// UTM Preservation - adds UTM params to key links\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n  var params = window.location.search;\n    if (!params) return; // No UTMs present, do nothing\n    \n      // Update links to these specific paths\n        // Note: /resources also catches all blog posts at /resources/post-name\n          var targetPaths = [\n              '/speed-report',\n                  '/resources',\n                      '/2025-intelligence-report',\n                          '/msms',\n                              'calendly.com'\n                                ];\n                                \n                                  document.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(function(link) {\n                                      var href = link.getAttribute('href');\n                                          if (!href) return;\n                                          \n                                              // Check if this link matches any target path\n                                                  var shouldUpdate = targetPaths.some(function(path) {\n                                                        return href.indexOf(path) > -1;\n                                                            });\n                                                            \n                                                                if (shouldUpdate) {\n                                                                      if (href.indexOf('?') > -1) {\n                                                                              link.setAttribute('href', href + '&' + params.substring(1));\n                                                                                    } else {\n                                                                                            link.setAttribute('href', href + params);\n                                                                                                  }\n                                                                                                      }\n                                                                                                        });\n                                                                                                        });\n                                                                                                        </script></body></html>"}
